#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:24
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_NOTHING\"]/text"
msgstr "你以某种冥想的状态走进伤痕累累的地方...盯着虚无。你决定最好不去管他们。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:27
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_GENERIC_1\"]/text"
msgstr "你发现烙疤者跪在地上……或许这是个让他们觉得放松的姿势？无论如何，他们开口道：“"
"很高兴见到你……同族。你有什么……需要吗？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:29
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "我有个问题。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:31
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "他们的眼睛微微眯起：“是……关于什么事？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:33
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "就是关于你！跟我多说说你自己的事。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:35
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "那道眯起的眼神舒缓开来，你能看到烙疤者的身躯放松了下来：“真是……出乎意料的请求"
"。你……想知道些什么？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:37
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "你是怎么偷来这些力量的？它们到底是什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:39
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“嗯……”他们闭上眼，思索了片刻这个问题。随后开口：“不止是我的身躯布满烙疤……我的"
"心智也是。我几乎记不得那天发生了什么……一台巨大的机械，漂浮在无尽深渊之中……但"
"也就仅此而已，一台机械。它……对我做了些什么，想要我臣服于它。我……证明了自己的"
"价值，它便认为我是晋升的合适人选。它……打错了算盘。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:41
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "然后呢？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:43
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他们脸上的笑容消失了：“然后……我就只记得这些了。伪神……赐予了我力量，而我挣脱了"
"它的掌控。我现在……被族人视作叛徒。被追杀，被流放……被抛弃。至于我的力量究竟是"
"什么……”他们的手开始虚化，在现实中忽隐忽现，随后又稳定下来，“我想，伪神本想赋"
"予我对它那……虚假虚空的统治权。我能操控它的黑暗……化身为它，并抵御它对我灵魂的"
"拉扯。”沉默片刻后，烙疤者重新露出微笑：“谢谢你……愿意过问这些，同族。但我必须"
"回去……继续冥想了。希望你的好奇心……得到了满足。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:49
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "在你还信奉黑暗之神的时候，你以前是什么样子的？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:51
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“我曾经……是一名猎手，虔诚得……近乎偏执。我献上的祭品……无人能及。无数生灵死在我"
"手中，皆为了伪神那……虚假的大义。我从不指望自己能真正……忏悔，或是原谅自己，但…"
"…若是能将伪神击倒，终结它的疯狂……我相信我便能安心安息。在那之前……”烙疤者笑了"
"笑，“……带路吧，同族。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:55
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "最喜欢的爱好？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:57
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他们眨了一下眼，又眨了一下，才终于开口回答：“我……喜欢看星星。”烙疤者的目光垂"
"到地面，你能感觉到他们……有些不好意思？“我……觉得那能让我平静下来。关于这件事……"
"我就说这么多。现在……请恕我失陪，我……还有些……非常重要的冥想要做。”你离开了房间"
"，心里还算满足，但又决定踮脚回来，从门口偷偷瞥一眼……你正好看见烙疤者正望向窗"
"外，随即他们转过身来，吓得你立刻沿着走廊逃开了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:65
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "不，只是过来看看你。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:67
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "“很……好吧。我没事。”他们只说了这么一句，便闭上了眼，干脆地结束了对话。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:72
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_GENERIC_2\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你来到烙疤者的门前，听见里面传来一阵剧烈的破碎声，于是你急忙冲进去，却看见……"
"烙疤者正站在一堆碎裂的玻璃器皿旁。“呃，同族！不是……你看到的那样！”这场景到底"
"像是什么？你也说不清楚，但你只觉得浑身不自在，于是一言不发地离开了房间……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:75
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_GENERIC_3\"]/text"
msgstr "烙疤者在货舱里，翻找着食物储备。注意到你的到来，他们开口道：“啊，同族。你……知"
"道我们把鱼放在哪儿吗？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:77
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_GENERIC_3\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "鱼？那难道不是……同类相食吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:79
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_GENERIC_3\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr "他们停下翻找，转过身看着你：“你……这话是什么意思？我……在你眼里看起来像条鱼吗？"
"”你觉得最好还是别回答，于是领着他们去放鱼的地方。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:84
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_GENERIC_4\"]/text"
msgstr "房间里一片漆黑，但你能感觉到烙疤者正在这里冥想……与其说是感觉，不如说你能听见"
"黑暗中传来他们那奇怪的、喉音沉重的吟唱。最好别打扰他们。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:87
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_GENERIC_5\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你在走廊里撞见烙疤者正在墙上画画。画得十分粗糙，但看起来是深渊潜者和他们的飞"
"船。烙疤者转过身来：“同族！我……希望你别介意。我找不到……纸，而我只想……尽力回忆"
"起来。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:89
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_GENERIC_5\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "记得？记得什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:91
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_GENERIC_5\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“回忆……我的过去，还有那些曾经出现在我生命里的人。遇见伪神之前的一切……都显得那"
"么模糊。可时不时地，还是会有碎片重新浮现……我不想再忘记，所以我想用画画的方式…"
"…把它们记下来。”“回忆”这个词在你脑海里莫名地回荡，可你想不通缘由。无论如何，"
"你被这份心意打动，便不再打扰，让烙疤者继续作画。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:96
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_THEHUNGER_1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你发现饥饿正从门缝里偷看烙疤者的房间——那明明是条密封的门缝……即便如此，它还是"
"发现了你被逮了个正着，开口道：“舰长。询——询——询问：目标：叛徒。请求：请求：请"
"求：”它不停地重复着“请求”这个词，直到你无奈离开房间……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:99
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_THEHUNGER_2\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"烙疤者和饥饿正待在一起放松，你心想……烙疤者开口道：“你……说话的方式很奇怪，就算"
"和你的同族相比也是如此。伪神到底……对你做了什么？”饥饿者微微震颤着，发出回荡的"
"声音：“上方。下——下——下方？目标——标——标：无处不在。状态：状态！：烙疤者。”烙"
"疤者似乎对此感到困扰，但没有再多说什么。两人沉默地坐着，你离开了房间，心里满"
"是困惑……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:102
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_VORTIGON_1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"沃蒂根盯着正在深度冥想的烙疤者。他看向你，开口问道：“既然他们没有可以祈祷的神"
"，为什么还要整天冥想？他们到底想达成什么？”你意识到，自己也不清楚答案。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:104
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_VORTIGON_1\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "这或许和他们的力量有关？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:106
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_VORTIGON_1\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他翻了个白眼：“那力量明明是他们从自己所谴责的存在那里偷来的！这家伙肯定藏了什"
"么事。我不知道到底是什么，但万一出了什么事……别说是没人提前警告过你们！在那之"
"前，我也只能相信你对他们的信任了。”沃蒂根又转回他那充满审视的注视，而你则回去"
"继续做你……刚才在做的事了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:111
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_VORTIGON_2\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"气氛十分紧张……你发现沃蒂根和烙疤者坐在一起，陷入了令人不安的沉默。最终，烙疤"
"者开口了：“你……不信任我。告诉我，牧师……你对伪神了解多少？”沃蒂根放声大笑：“从"
"没听说过他们！确实是伪神，可他们的力量却无比真实……而你正心甘情愿地用这力量为"
"自己谋利。告诉我，叛徒……你懂什么是信任？懂什么是信仰，什么是忠诚？”烙疤者的脸"
"上瞬间燃起怒火……那是你从未在他们身上见过的愤怒。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:113
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_VORTIGON_2\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "打断。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:115
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_VORTIGON_2\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"烙疤者的脸色平复下来，看向你：“同族！真……巧啊，在这儿遇见你。在……你的船上……”"
"沃蒂根一言不发，凝视着烙疤者那只完好的眼睛。你化解了冲突，可此刻气氛却尴尬到"
"了极点……烙疤者咳嗽一声：“我……我想我该走了。我们……改天再继续吧，沃蒂根。”他们"
"站起身，沃蒂根回应道：“好，我想会的。在那之前……”沃蒂根闭上双眼，双手合十做出"
"祈祷的姿势，“……我还有神明要侍奉。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:120
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_SLOCKNOG_1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"斯洛克诺格与烙疤者似乎借着各自一支香烟渐渐熟络，他们一边一同抽烟一边交谈，“能"
"遇见另一位流亡者真是太好了。我还以为，我是唯一一个被自己同族唾弃的人！”烙疤者"
"对他轻笑一声，“我……的确认为我们的处境有着很大的……不同，君主，可是……我必须认同"
"，这样很好。极少有人……对我如此友善。”两人继续你来我往地交谈着，而你面带微笑离"
"开了房间。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:123
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_SCARRED_ALKALI_1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你找到的并不是烙疤者，而是阿尔科莱，他心烦意乱地滚到你面前，“舰长……那个恶棍，"
"烙疤者，他不肯叫我的名字！执意要叫我‘那个科学玩意儿’！你敢信吗？我知道其他种"
"族通常都很原始，但这也太过分了。对我来说，对他们来说都是……”他垂头丧气地滚走了"
"。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:145
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_NOTHING\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"饥饿似乎正在房间里撕咬着地板……他们转向你，“舰长。出——现——麻——烦——了：饥饿。解"
"决办法？解决办法？解决办法！：快。”看来他们想让你立刻启动这艘飞船。马上。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:148
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_GENERIC_1\"]/text"
msgstr "想要找到他们并不难……你循着地板上的抓痕，最终在走廊中央找到了正原地打转的饥饿"
"。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:150
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "引起他们的注意。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:152
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"饥饿的脸转向你，而身体的其余部分仍在不停旋转，“协议错误：‘问候’协议已损坏。执"
"行备用协议：告别协议。再——再——再见，舰长？舰长！再——见，舰长！”说完，你看着他"
"们爬走，在转过拐角时，视线依旧牢牢锁着你。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:156
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "由着他们用自己古怪的方式行事吧。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:158
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "转念一想，你实在没什么心情去和“饥饿”说话……你任由他们继续古怪地旋转。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:163
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_GENERIC_2\"]/text"
msgstr "你在货舱里发现饥饿正在撕咬食物补给。可惜，但你觉得……它们先吃掉零食总比盯上你"
"要好……无论如何，最好还是别去管它们的狂暴行径。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:166
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_GENERIC_3\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"一番搜寻之后，你撞见饥饿正从墙上啃下一大块。你确信这只是块无关紧要的墙体。这"
"似乎让它满足了，它的脸转向你，“目标……目标？目标！：饥饿。状态：已满足。请求："
"请求：请求：说话，舰长！舰长，说、说话！”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:168
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_GENERIC_3\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "呃，嗨。你好吗，饥饿？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:170
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_GENERIC_3\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“向目标问好：你！你也好，舰 —— 长！舰长？舰长。重复状态：饥饿…… 是…… 是！已满"
"足。” 过了一会儿，它轻轻晃动了一下，“状态更新？更新：饥饿不…… 不…… 不满足了。"
"不满足。解决方式：吞噬！再、再、再见，舰长……？再见。” 它钻进自己在墙上啃出的"
"洞里消失了，只留下你暗自思索这艘飞船到底有多少部分是可以牺牲的……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:175
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_TURZIL_1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你撞见图尔齐尔正在观察饥饿，又戳又碰。你正准备开口，图尔齐尔的手臂就从肩膀上"
"被扯了下来，饥饿对他的触碰做出反应，将手臂一口吞噬。即便如此，图尔齐尔却显得"
"毫不在意。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:177
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_TURZIL_1\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "呃……这里一切都还好吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:179
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_TURZIL_1\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"图尔齐尔转向你，“你的眼睛——出问题了吗，舰长？我看不出这里有什么‘还好’的。”他"
"转回头看向饥饿，“这可不是简单的谐合联结受损，这也不是[普通的]半械族。这是[许"
"多]半械族，在受苦。被[黑暗]力量强行束缚在一起。这种力量我——无法——理解。”饥饿"
"扭动了一会儿，然后开口道：“饥饿：黑暗！黑暗，黑、黑暗……谐合：暂时稳住？暂时稳"
"住！侵蚀：消失？消失！代价：已付出。已付出，已付出，已付出！足够了。”图尔齐尔"
"斥责道，“你只是从一个[残忍的]主人换到了另一个。你依旧——被困——在这种状态里：不"
"比我，或任何其他半械族自由多少。”他发出一声机械的叹息，转身离开，“只能——希望—"
"—他们还有机会：在某个地方。祝你——好运——能找到，舰长。”只剩下你和饥饿待在原地"
"，它似乎又回去啃咬图尔齐尔的手臂了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:184
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_TURZIL_2\"]/text"
msgstr "你走进饥饿的房间，却惊讶地发现站在那里的是图尔齐尔。他似乎正在检查这间房间，"
"以及饥饿入住后所造成的破坏……而破坏之处数不胜数。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:186
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_TURZIL_2\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "咳嗽。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:188
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_TURZIL_2\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "图尔齐尔似乎吓了一跳，但也只是一瞬间，“舰长。询问：你对谐离有什么看法？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:190
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_TURZIL_2\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "他们的所作所为是不对的。处在谐合之下的半械族，不该为它的行径而承受苦难。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:192
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_TURZIL_2\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“对某些人来说，被剥夺自我可以被称作苦难。按照这个逻辑，这位饥饿为何要牺牲自身"
"？化为众多个体？化为无思之物……”他顿了顿，“……或许在失去自我的过程中，他们试图"
"拯救更多存在。一场大胆的赌局。结果，仍有待观察。我的一部分祈祷他们保持这般模"
"样。另一部分……却仍怀有希望。希望谐合终将覆灭。”图尔齐尔离开了房间，四周一片寂"
"静……唯有地板下传来啃噬的声响。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:196
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_TURZIL_2\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "我支持他们。半械族理应摆脱谐合的控制，而半械分离者袖手旁观是无法让他们获得自"
"由的。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:198
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_TURZIL_2\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“这话很对，可惜是这样。但问题依然存在：这是一场为了半械族、对抗半械族的战争。"
"更不用说他们所做的黑暗交易。就算他们赢了，他们真的能自由地做自己吗？能摆脱他"
"们的束缚吗？”你对这句话眨了眨眼，有些困惑，图尔齐尔注意到了，“是枷锁。那个词"
"是枷锁。我还在习惯用这种比喻。”他有些尴尬地离开了房间，四周一片寂静……只有地板"
"下传来啃咬的声音。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:202
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_TURZIL_2\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "我宁愿不掺和进来。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:204
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_TURZIL_2\"]/choice[1]/event/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“你的行动背叛了你的言辞。我和这位饥饿此刻站在这里，已经脱离了谐合的掌控。推测"
"：你只是太过谦逊了，舰长？”你脸颊一红，忍不住笑了出来……你觉得自己还挺厉害的。"
"图尔齐尔满意地离开了房间，四周一片寂静……只有地板下传来啃咬的声音。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:210
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_TURZIL_2\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "由他去吧。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:212
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_TURZIL_2\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "你让图尔齐尔独自留下，回头继续寻找饥饿。你没有找到它们，但却渐渐对地板下传来"
"的啃咬声习以为常。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:217
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_OOJ_1\"]/text"
msgstr "在你前往饥饿房间的路上，你发现它和OOJ在走廊中央对峙……你该担心吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:219
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_OOJ_1\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "干预。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:221
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_OOJ_1\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你实在不确定到底该怎么介入，于是就这么站在了它们中间……它们离得都非常近。你能"
"听到OOJ的身体发出规律的轻响，还有饥饿在啃咬地板的声音。最后，它们似乎都开始后"
"退……慢慢地。饥饿始终没有移开与你对视的目光，OOJ也始终保持着它那种OOJ式的注视"
"。最终，轻响和啃咬声渐渐消失，只剩下你一个人……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:225
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_OOJ_1\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "观察。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:227
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_OOJ_1\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"过了一会儿什么都没发生，直到OOJ开始震动……接着，饥饿也跟着共振起来。你意识到大"
"事不妙，它们的震动频率不断加快，互相呼应。OOJ的“啪 啪 啪”声越来越快，饥饿发出"
"的奇怪啃噬声也同样急促……你这是在见证一台粒子加速器的诞生吗？你还能逃掉吗？这"
"艘飞船里还有安全的地方吗？这个星域里还有安全的地方吗？这个现实？这个多元宇宙"
"？就在你思考这些问题时，两个团状物突然同时停止移动，完全违背了惯性。OOJ滑向一"
"边，饥饿滑向另一边，直到双双消失在视线中……你刚才究竟目睹了什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:232
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_OOJ_2\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"尽管你竭尽全力，还是到处都找不到饥饿。你确实听到天花板上方传来一阵奇怪的“啪 "
"啪 啪”声，地板底下也相应地传来一阵怪异的“嘎吱 嘎吱 嘎吱”声……但这大概没什么。"
"不过是诡异的太空幻觉之类的东西罢了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:235
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_THE_HUNGER_ANOINTED_1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"啃咬声让你察觉到饥饿在飞船另一头的位置，可你惊讶地发现强选者也在那里。他们正"
"来回传递一大块金属，轮流啃食……饥饿开口道：“目标：强——强选者？强选者。状态：饥"
"饿？也饥饿？”强选者回答：“没错，奇怪的半械造物。我们不必独自饥饿，不必独自腐"
"朽。在一起，我们可吞噬一切。”饥饿闻言兴奋地扭动起来，你担心自身安全，随即离开"
"了房间……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:255
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_NOTHING\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"当你走近愚者时，他的姿态缩了起来，“你难道没有什么值得……值得交谈的人吗……？别管"
"我……”他神情沮丧地飘走了，你在心里记下，要给你的船员安排一些心理疏导课程。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:258
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"走进愚者的房间，里面看上去空无一人……直到你听见头顶传来一声闷响。抬头望去，你"
"发现愚者正漂浮在天花板上，一遍又一遍地慢慢撞上去，再弹开。就算他察觉到了你在"
"场，也没有表现出来。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:260
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_1\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "嘿，呃……你还好吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:262
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_1\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr "他转过来面对着你，仍旧在天花板上撞来撞去，“嗯，我没事……谢……谢谢……”尽管他避开"
"了你的目光，却没有再转过身去。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:264
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_1\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "我才不信呢。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:266
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_1\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"愚者再次与你对视，语气严肃了几分：“真的，我没事。我只是……有时候会变成这样。”"
"他沉默了片刻，叹了口气继续说道：“就算我想振作起来，也由不得我。有些事……实在压"
"得我喘不过气。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:268
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_1\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "是什么事？我能帮上什么忙吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:270
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_1\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他似乎花了片刻整理思绪，才回答道：“你已经帮得够多了，舰长。我只是在和自己进行"
"一场精神斗争……”你注意到他的目光落在了地板上，“不过……如果你能帮我，呃……从这里"
"下去，我会很感激的。”他伸出了手。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:272
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_1\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "握住他的手，帮他下来。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:274
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_1\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "你握住他的手，一阵不安感席卷全身，然后你感觉到……一片虚无。那感觉来得快去得也"
"快，愚者期待地看着你：“舰长？你还好吗？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:276
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_1\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "嗯，我只是……感觉到了点东西。这里很安全，对吧？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:278
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_1\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "愚者愣了一下，眨了眨眼，随即猛地抽回手，语气里满是关切：“等等，你到底感觉到了"
"什么？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:280
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_1\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "我……我也说不准。我只是刚才感觉有点不对劲。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:282
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_1\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他稍稍放松了一些，好吧，如果你担心的是这个，那灵魂瘟疫并没有威胁。它听命于我…"
"…尽管我痛恨这一点。我担心的是黑暗之神……它仍对我有一定的影响。如果你感觉到了什"
"么，那很可能意味着它在试图搞些小动作，我不会再让任何人因为我而让自己陷入危险"
"。你看着愚者深吸一口气，再缓缓吐出，身体慢慢飘回地板。至少还是谢谢你安抚了我"
"。不过……抱歉是我目光太短浅了。我不想自己被黑暗之神利用，再去实施它的阴谋。我"
"以后会多加小心。愚者飘出了房间，只留下你暗自思索……黑暗之神到底想要什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:286
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_1\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "我……刚才感觉到我们之间，很近。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:288
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_1\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "他的身体微微倾斜，像是有些困惑，“嗯……是啊？那又怎么样？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:290
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_1\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我们以前从来没有真正靠近过。我一直以为这是不安全的。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:292
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_1\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他似乎思考了一会儿才回答，“好吧，如果你担心的是这个，那灵魂瘟疫并没有威胁。它"
"听从我的命令……尽管我很讨厌这件事。我担心的是黑暗之神……它仍然对我有一定的影响"
"。如果你感觉到了什么，那很可能意味着它在试图搞些小动作，我不会让任何人再因为"
"我而让自己陷入危险。”你看着愚者深吸一口气，然后缓缓吐出，身体慢慢飘回地板。“"
"至少还是谢谢你安抚我。不过……抱歉是我想得太浅了。我不想自己被黑暗之神利用，去"
"实施它的另一个阴谋。我以后会更加小心的。”愚者飘出了房间，只留下你暗自思索……黑"
"暗之神到底想要什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:302
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_1\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "犹豫。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:304
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_1\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "你站在那里，盯着他的手，过了片刻。这让愚者显得有些不安，但他始终没有开口。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:306
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_1\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "你触碰别人对你来说安全吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:308
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_1\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他想了一会儿，收回了手，“好吧，如果你担心的是这个，那灵魂瘟疫并没有威胁。它听"
"从我的命令……尽管我很痛恨这件事。可即便如此，谁也不知道黑暗之神会试图耍什么手"
"段。我还是离大家远一点，或许才是最好的选择。”你看着愚者深吸一口气，然后缓缓吐"
"出，身体慢慢飘回地板。“至少还是谢谢你安抚了我。不过……抱歉是我想得太浅了。我不"
"想自己被黑暗之神利用，去实施它的另一个阴谋。我以后会更加小心的。”愚者飘出了房"
"间，只留下你暗自思索……黑暗之神到底想要什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:312
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_1\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "甲壳族有手吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:314
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_1\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "他似乎被你的问题弄糊涂了，“有啊？不然我们怎么做事？你至少见过我们修理东西吧？"
"”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:316
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_1\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "是啊，我就是……好像从来没认真想过这个问题？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:318
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_1\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"愚者笑了起来，这般难得的模样让你的心也跟着暖了起来。“好吧，我们确实有手。”他"
"收回手，深吸一口气再缓缓吐出，身体慢慢飘回地板。“谢谢你逗我开心，舰长……你真傻"
"。”他顿了顿，又有些慌乱地补充，“不过是好的那种！”愚者连忙飘出了房间，你能感觉"
"到，他的甲壳之下一定涨红了脸。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:324
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_1\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "你……的手真可爱。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:326
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_1\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"愚者被这句话彻底惊到了，结结巴巴地半天说不出一句完整的话：“我——我的——什么？我"
"的手？你……你真的……我……”他的呼吸越来越急促，你能看到他的身体不受控制地慢慢飘回"
"地板，“……我、我得走了，舰长！谢、谢谢你，呃，逗我开心！”他急匆匆地飘出房间，"
"一路上还撞到了好几样东西，你忍不住在心里想着……他是真的很可爱。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:336
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_1\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "好吧，好吧……我就不追问了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:338
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_1\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "虽然他的话听着并不怎么让人信服，但你也不会强迫自己的船员敞开心扉。愚者对你的"
"理解表示感谢，你便留下他一个人……继续飘在天花板附近。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:345
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_2\"]/text"
msgstr "当你走近愚者的房间时，注意到门的缝隙里透出奇异的、彩虹般的微光……多元宇宙里到"
"底发生什么事了？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:347
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_2\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "这应该挺正常的。进去吧。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:349
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_2\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你伸手按在门上，一阵剧痛瞬间贯穿手臂，你被猛地弹开好几英尺。身体重重撞在墙上"
"，你茫然地躺在地上好一会儿，才挣扎着站起身。勉强站稳后，你觉得还是晚点再来比"
"较好……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:353
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_2\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "才不要，去他的吧。我今天才不要掺和任何诡异的外星破事。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:355
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_2\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "不管里面到底在搞什么鬼，你都没兴趣知道。你小心翼翼地从门口后退，而那扇门只是"
"依旧闪烁着微光，像是在回应你的举动。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:360
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_3\"]/text"
msgstr "不管里面到底在搞什么鬼，你都没兴趣知道。你小心翼翼地从门口后退，而那扇门只是"
"依旧闪烁着微光，像是在回应你的举动。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:362
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_3\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "我就是想见你！你在这里干什么呢？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:364
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_3\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他似乎被吓了一跳，有些局促不安地回答：“我只是……呃，有点饿……作为一种物质病毒，"
"灵魂瘟疫通常让我几乎什么都能吃，可是……有时候它会特别想吃某样东西。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:366
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_3\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "特别的东西？比如？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:368
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_3\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "“比如……嗯……纸板……”愚者移开视线，从平时漂浮的高度往下沉了一点，轻轻撞到了地板"
"上。“你、你不会……刚好知道我们把纸板放在哪儿吧，舰长？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:370
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_3\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我还真不知道。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:372
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_3\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他把身体往地板上压得更沉了，语气沮丧地回答：“没、没关系，反正这也只是个莫名其"
"妙的想吃的念头……至少、谢谢你愿意来找我说话。回头见，舰长……”愚者合上了刚才一直"
"在翻找的容器，没有像往常那样滚动或是漂浮，而是让身体贴着地面，一点点蹭着离开"
"了房间。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:380
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_3\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "哦，我只是路过而已。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:382
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_3\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"这话似乎让他松了口气，语气也轻快了些：“哦，好。那、那我们晚点再聊吧，舰长。回"
"头见……也许吧……”愚者一直望着你，直到你离开货舱，之后你便听见他又开始翻找东西。"
"你不禁好奇，他到底在找什么……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:387
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_GENERIC_4\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你发现愚者正在摆弄自己的甲壳，一边测量一边取样。他看起来陷入了沉思，并没有注"
"意到你走近，于是你觉得还是下次再来比较好。就在你离开房间时，听见他自言自语：“"
"这……是青色还是青绿色？上周还是青色的，可是……现在很难分辨了……”不一直都是这样吗"
"？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:390
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_ALKALI_1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"阿尔科莱似乎正在拿愚者做实验，而后者只是沮丧地坐在那里。前者一边说话，一边不"
"停戳弄试探：“你知道吗，当我听说和伊普西隆的通讯中断时，我还以为你们这帮人只是"
"把自己炸飞了之类的。我万万没想到事情的真相！告诉我，那是什么感觉？”愚者别过头"
"去，却被阿尔科莱转了回来，他轻轻叹了口气：“什么是什么感觉？寒冷？那些……声音？"
"还是……那场种族灭绝……？”阿尔科莱嗤笑一声：“不，显然不是这么微不足道的事。我是"
"说接近我的天才头脑！这灵魂瘟疫的玩意儿相当厉害！当然了，是跟那些不如我的东西"
"比起来。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:392
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_ALKALI_1\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:394
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_ALKALI_1\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你能感觉到房间里的温度微微上升，一丝真切的鄙夷正从愚者身上散发出来。他怒视着"
"阿尔科莱：“你觉得，当它摧残我们同伴的心智、操控他们的躯体时，他们会觉得这很了"
"不起吗？如果你……遭遇了同样的下场，你也会觉得它很厉害吗？”阿尔科莱微微一怔，暂"
"时停下了手中的实验。随后他继续动作：“反正我不用担心这种事，不是吗？只要你能控"
"制住它就行。你，呃，你控制得住它，对吧？”愚者放松了些许，恢复了平日的神态：“"
"我已经尽我所能了……如果你是想问这个，它暂时没有威胁。只是……那些失控的物质病毒"
"菌株仍在外面，伤害着无辜的人……”他垂落肩头，阿尔科莱拍了拍他的后背：“那就更有"
"理由乖乖坐着，让我继续实验了！能治好这种病毒的人，除了我还能有谁！”愚者像是默"
"认了，只是又叹了口气，两个甲壳族便陷入了沉默。你决定把空间留给他们，让他们继"
"续进行实验。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:399
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_ALKALI_2\"]/text"
msgstr "虽然你找不到愚者，却找到了阿尔科莱，他似乎也在找愚者。他转向你：“喂，变元者，"
"你有没有见过那个搞砸了的实验体？我是说，那个伊普西隆的弃子。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:401
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_ALKALI_2\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "你是说愚者吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:403
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_ALKALI_2\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"阿尔科莱轻笑一声：“很高兴我们想到一块儿去了，不过‘愚者’可不是我会用的说法。我"
"会选个更狠点的称呼，比如‘彻头彻尾无可救药的蠢货’之类的。对了，你见过他吗？”他"
"还是一如既往地“讨人喜欢”……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:405
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_ALKALI_2\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "是啊……我没见过他，我自己也在找他。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:407
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_ALKALI_2\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他叹了口气，转身滚走了：“就知道你也派不上用场。好吧，如果你真见到他，告诉他，"
"他那物质病毒又把我的牙刷变成了一团有自我意识、吞噬物质的憎恶体。麻烦提醒他别"
"再用我的牙刷，不然我就把他的牙刷改成临时炸弹。”阿尔科莱转过拐角，只留下你在心"
"里纳闷……甲壳族真的有牙齿吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:414
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_TULLY_1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"塔利和愚者正专注地下着一盘激烈的国际象棋，塔利看起来比愚者投入得多。你不太看"
"得懂棋局，但塔利走了一步棋，显得颇为得意：“你知道吗，我现在很少有时间下棋了，"
"但想当年我可是天生的高手！能放松一下，重温那段时光，哪怕只有一会儿，也感觉很"
"好。”愚者摆弄着一枚棋子，然后也走了一步：“过去的日子……真的简单多了。不过我从"
"来都不怎么喜欢国际象棋。但我觉得……我现在玩得还挺开心的。”塔利又走了一步，愚者"
"毫不犹豫地应对落子：“这……这是将死了，对吧……？”塔利扫视了一遍棋盘，笑了起来：“"
"还真是！唉，看来我手感生疏了！下次你可得再让我挑战一次，好不好？”愚者的心情显"
"然好了不少，一边收拾棋盘一边回答：“当然，我玩得很开心。谢谢你，塔利……”看着两"
"人心满意足地离开房间，你很高兴，即便船员里最悲观的人也能拥有这样愉悦的时刻。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:417
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_THESCARRED_1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你推门进去，正好看见烙疤者在检查愚者的身体，他皮肤上的虹彩在对方触碰下似乎在"
"退缩。愚者转向对方，语气里带着迟疑：“我……从没见过物质病毒对别人的触碰有过这样"
"的反应。你……到底是谁？”烙疤者叹了口气，微微后退：“我也希望……我能回答这个问题"
"。伪神……夺走了我的名字，就像夺走你的一样。我们两人的力量……都是它创造的，可是…"
"…它们却好像在互相排斥。到底……是为了什么？”两人沉默地坐了一会儿，陷入沉思，你"
"觉得最好还是不要打扰他们的思考。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:420
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_THEHUNGER_1\"]/text"
msgstr "穿过走廊时，你突然停下脚步，惊讶地看见愚者站在那里，朝你大喊：“舰长！！！不管"
"你做什么，都别动！”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:422
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_THEHUNGER_1\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "什么？怎么了？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:424
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_THEHUNGER_1\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他打断了你的话：“嘘——！听着！有东西……在船上，就在这里！”你拼命凝神去听。在飞"
"船各处运转的嗡鸣之下，传来一阵几乎听不见的声音：远处传来嘎吱、嘎吱、嘎吱的声"
"响……这声音你无论在哪里都能认出来！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:426
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_THEHUNGER_1\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "哦，那只是饥饿而已。没什么好担心的。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:428
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_THEHUNGER_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"愚者吓了一跳：“没什么好担心的——那东西正在啃穿船壳啊？而且……你确定这安全吗？”"
"你点了点头，他困惑地飘了起来：“看来我们每个人多多少少……都有自己的怪异之处。看"
"看我，说得好像我自身的危险性就更低似的……”愚者转过拐角，继续在心里纠结着自我价"
"值，只剩下你和那熟悉的啃噬声待在原地。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:435
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_FOOLISH_THEHEROINE_1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"一支长矛从你头顶飞掠而过，在你身后呼啸着扎进墙壁数英尺深，发出一声沉闷的巨响"
"。女杰大喊：“给我站住！只要你别再……跑了！这一下很快的！”她似乎正在追逐愚者创"
"造的一具灵魂瘟疫躯壳……你可不想被她这股正义怒火波及，于是立刻转身走开，免得那"
"些能击穿船壳的长矛下一个目标就是你。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:458
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_NOTHING\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"大臣正在摆弄他的装甲，见你走近便抬起空闲的那只手：“抱歉，变元者，我现在很忙。"
"装甲核心又出故障了，我必须在它撕裂时空结构、把整艘飞船扯碎之前把它稳定住。”是"
"啊，这……听起来确实很要紧。你还是晚点再来吧。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:461
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_1\"]/text"
msgstr "你正在寻找大臣时，舰船的能源短暂闪烁熄灭。片刻之后，灯光再次熄灭，你听到你要"
"找的那个人怒吼道：“你现在为什么这么贪心？你到底还想要多少？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:463
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "冲到他身边。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:465
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你循着他的声音走去，当电力恢复时，他转过身面对你：“哦，变元者。抱歉，呃，舰船"
"系统不太稳定。装甲饿了。”他没再多做解释，就回头继续之前的事，你注意到从他战甲"
"延伸出的管线……正直接从舰船反应堆中汲取能量。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:467
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "这样安全吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:469
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他再次转向你，毫不掩饰自己的不耐烦：“当然安全。不安全我会这么做吗？我说过了，"
"装甲饿了，我想你也不会喜欢其他的解决办法。”他摆弄着其中一根管线，然后又回头瞪"
"了你一眼，“没事的，变元者。我不会把飞船炸掉，也不会做出你担心的那些事。你现在"
"可以走了；我必须在我们下一场冲突前把这事处理好。”撇开他那居高临下的态度不谈，"
"在你离开房间、走向走廊时，你原本还相信他。可就在这时，能源忽明忽暗，那份信心"
"也开始微微动摇。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:475
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "不管他。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:477
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他听起来过得很艰难，你也清楚他向来不喜欢被人打扰。你不再打扰他，转而在飞船的"
"走廊里闲逛，心里相信他无论在做什么，应该都不会有事。灯光依旧忽明忽暗，闪烁不"
"停，而那份信心也开始一点点减弱。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:482
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_2\"]/text"
msgstr "你在寻找大臣时，发现他正在休息室里喝咖啡。你不记得这艘船上有咖啡机……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:484
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_2\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "你从哪儿弄来的这个？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:486
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_2\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他侧过头，又喝了一口咖啡，示意你看过去，你便走上前去……要是你嘴里正含着咖啡，"
"看到房间里这一片狼藉，绝对会当场喷出来。柜台上摊着一台面目全非的诡异装置，散"
"落的咖啡豆是它唯一还能看出用途的痕迹。装置周围的空间都被烧焦，机器残存的部分"
"早已彻底扭曲、碎裂。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:488
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_2\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你……临时做了个爆炸装置，就为了煮咖啡？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:490
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_2\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "他放下杯子，得意一笑：“也可以这么说。天才吧？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:492
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_2\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "可是，你从哪儿弄来的咖啡豆？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:494
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_2\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他又把头歪向房间另一边，再次吸引了你的目光。你盯着那边那个怪物看了一会儿——一"
"半是可怖的黏液生物，一半又像是咖啡植株，然后伸手拿起大臣的咖啡。他没有阻止，"
"你重重地喝了一大口。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:496
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_2\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "把咖啡喷得到处都是。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:498
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_2\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你想不出更合适的回应。大臣看上去只觉得好笑，你放下他的杯子转身离开房间，两人"
"都没再提起他在这里造出的这些恐怖东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:509
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_3\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"虽然找到他并不难，但你还没说上几句话，大臣就把你赶出了他的房间，还给了你一张"
"清单，让你去取他需要的东西……据说是为了他的实验，可这清单看起来更像是一份购物"
"清单。他难道没有手下可以处理这些事吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:511
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_3\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "看看清单。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:513
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_3\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"一张横格纸上用墨水写着大臣的清单：\n"
"\n"
"鸡蛋\n"
"鸡蛋\n"
"糖\n"
"面粉\n"
"过量时空物质稳定装置（青绿色）\n"
"鸡蛋"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:522
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_3\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "好，行。去把大臣要的东西拿来。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:524
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_3\"]/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"烹饪用的食材倒不难凑齐，可那个时空相关的玩意儿就显得有点……太奇特了。你能找到"
"的最接近的东西只有青蓝色食用色素，最后决定把他要的东西放在门外，免得他让你解"
"释。当天晚些时候，你从他房间里传来大喊：“不对，不对！我说的是青绿色！青绿色！"
"”这差别真的有那么重要吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:528
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_3\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "我是他老妈吗？把清单揉成一团扔掉。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:530
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_3\"]/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"把那张纸扔到一边，纸上突然爆发出一阵强光；等你的视线恢复时，眼前的景象让你更"
"加目瞪口呆……揉皱的纸变成了清单上列出的所有东西。你不想多问，更不想靠近那个散"
"发着诡异震动、一看就知道是时空装置的神秘物品，于是把这堆东西放在了大臣的门外"
"。当天晚些时候，你听到他房间里传来怒吼：“不对，不对！我说的是青绿色！青绿色！"
"”你还以为这就是……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:537
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_4\"]/text"
msgstr "你在房间里找到了大臣，他正跪在地上查看一张照片。就算他注意到了你，也没有表现"
"出来。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:539
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "清了清嗓子。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:541
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "他叹了口气，转向你：“是啊，我知道你在这儿。我要是聋了才会察觉不到……你真有什么"
"要紧事，非得打断我的沉思不可吗？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:543
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你的……沉思？你到底在想什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:545
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"大臣打量了你一番，仿佛在衡量你值不值得交谈，随后又叹了口气，重新看向手中的照"
"片：“是……我的女儿。我一直都惦记着她。这件事我已经跟你说得够多了，只是……有件事"
"我想问问你。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:547
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我？我可以试着回答，不过我不确定能帮上你什么。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:549
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "他点了点头：“我要的只是一个答案。”大臣随即直视着你的眼睛，眼底带着一丝空洞：“"
"你相信你所看到的一切吗？相信别人告诉你的一切吗？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:551
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "这问题……问得太模糊了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:553
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"我们的处境、我们之间的关系，一切都是模糊的。即便如此，在这些事情上我们仍必须"
"相信自己的判断。这是对话中他第一次眨了眨眼：“所以告诉我。你相信别人告诉你的一"
"切吗？关于那场叛乱，关于那场风暴，或是……任何事。简单说：你相信我们这个现实是"
"真实的吗？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:555
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "是。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:557
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"人们常常会脑补模拟现实或是昏迷引发的梦境之类的想法，但你能感觉到，大臣指的完"
"全是另一回事。某种更黑暗、更凶险的事。不过他似乎对你的回答很满意，随即再次转"
"向手中的照片：“很好，变元者。没事了。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:559
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "等等，真的假的？你抛出这么一个不祥的问题，然后就不肯再多解释了？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:561
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他轻声笑了笑：“你还真是容易被吓到，不是吗？这只是我最近在沿着眼前这条路走下去"
"时，一直萦绕在心头的事。纵然我有过人的才智，有这该死的铠甲赋予我的力量，可当"
"我盲目遵从那些指令时，只觉得自己不过是一颗棋子。我就这么悬在一种虚无的状态里"
"，不断追寻一个或许永远都不会到来的结果。我……原本以为我们在这一点上是相似的。”"
"他深深地叹了口气：“也许是我判断错了。又或者，我只是太过阴郁，自寻烦恼。不管怎"
"样，我想站在这里和你谈论这些，也没法弄明白事情的真相。当然，我并无冒犯之意。”"
"好吧……听出这话里的暗示，你留下大臣独自进行那些诡异的沉思，可他的一部分疑虑，"
"也跟着你一同离开了房间。他到底在怀疑什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:567
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "是的！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:569
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"人们常会去设想模拟现实或是昏迷引发的梦境这类概念，但你能感觉到，大臣所指的完"
"全是另一回事。某种更黑暗、更凶险的事。不过他似乎对你的回答很满意，随即再次看"
"向手中的照片：“很好，变元者。没事了。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:571
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "等等，真的吗？你抛出这么一个不祥的问题，然后就不肯详细解释了？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:573
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他轻声笑了笑：“你还真是容易受惊，不是吗？这只是我最近沿着眼前这条路走下去时，"
"一直萦绕在心头的事。纵然我天资过人，又有这副该死的铠甲赋予我力量，可当我盲目"
"遵从下达的命令时，只觉得自己不过是一颗棋子。我就这般悬在虚无的境地之中，不断"
"追寻一个或许永远都不会到来的结果。我……原本以为我们在这一点上是相似的。”他深深"
"地叹了口气：“也许是我判断错了。又或者，我只是太过阴郁，自寻烦恼。无论如何，我"
"想站在这里和你谈论这些，也没法弄清真相。当然，我并无冒犯之意。”好吧……听出了其"
"中的暗示，你留下大臣独自进行那些诡异的沉思，可他的一部分疑虑，也跟着你一同离"
"开了房间。他到底在怀疑什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:579
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "怎么了？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:581
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"人们常会去设想模拟现实或是昏迷引发的梦境这类概念，但你能感觉到，大臣所指的完"
"全是另一回事。某种更黑暗、更凶险的事。不过他似乎对你的回答很满意，随即再次看"
"向手中的照片：“很好，变元者。没事了。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:583
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[3]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "等等，真的吗？你抛出这么一个不祥的问题，然后就不肯再多解释了？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:585
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[3]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他轻声笑了笑：“你还真是容易受惊，不是吗？这只是我最近沿着眼前这条路走下去时，"
"一直萦绕在心头的事。纵然我天资过人，又有这副该死的铠甲赋予我力量，可当我盲目"
"遵从下达的命令时，只觉得自己不过是一颗棋子。我就这般悬在虚无的境地之中，不断"
"追寻一个或许永远都不会到来的结果。我……原本以为我们在这一点上是相似的。”他深深"
"地叹了口气：“也许是我判断错了。又或者，我只是太过阴郁，自寻烦恼。无论如何，我"
"想站在这里和你谈论这些，也没法弄清真相。当然，我并无冒犯之意。”好吧……听出了其"
"中的暗示，你留下大臣独自进行那些诡异的沉思，可他的一部分疑虑，也跟着你一同离"
"开了房间。他到底在怀疑什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:591
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[4]/text"
msgstr "对对对对对对对对对对对对对对对对对对对对对"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:593
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[4]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"人们常常会设想模拟现实或是昏迷引发的梦境之类的概念，但你能感觉到，大臣所指的"
"完全是另一回事，某种更黑暗、更凶险的事。可他似乎对你的回答很满意，随即再次看"
"向手中的照片：“很好，变元者。没事了。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:595
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[4]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "等等，真的吗？你抛出这么一个不祥的问题，然后却不肯详细解释？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:597
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[4]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他轻笑一声：“你还真是容易被吓到，不是吗？这只是我近来沿着眼前这条道路前行时，"
"一直萦绕心头的事。纵然我才智过人，又有这副可憎的铠甲赋予我力量，可当我盲目遵"
"从下达的命令时，只觉得自己不过是一枚棋子。我就这般身处虚无的境地，不断追寻一"
"个或许永远都不会到来的结果。我……原本以为我们在这一点上是相似的。”他深深叹了口"
"气：“也许是我判断错了。又或许，我只是太过阴郁，自寻烦恼。无论如何，我想站在这"
"里和你谈论这些，也无法探明真相。当然，我并无冒犯之意。”好吧……你领会了暗示，留"
"下大臣独自进行那些诡异的沉思，可他的一部分疑虑，也随你一同离开了房间。他究竟"
"在怀疑什么？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:611
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "不管他了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:613
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "你觉得他看上去很忙，于是悄悄退了出去。大臣自始至终都没有动过，而你心里不禁疑"
"惑，到底是什么事让他如此心事重重。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:618
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_5\"]/text"
msgstr "你走近大臣的房门时，能听见屋内传来一阵诡异的吟唱，那些颂歌仿佛要钻进你的脑海"
"里。无尽的不安涌上心头，你开始怀疑自己是否该进去。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:620
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_5\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "稳住心神，推门进去。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:622
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_5\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你紧贴着房门，做好了应对脑海中能想到的任何状况的准备……却唯独没料到眼前这一幕"
"。大臣和其他几位身披斗篷的风暴信徒围坐在一张圆形咖啡桌旁，看得出来他们正在玩"
"某种桌面游戏。房间另一侧的收音机正大声播放着你先前听到的吟唱。大臣转过头，尽"
"力在嘈杂的音量中对你喊道：“变元者？你有什么理由打断我们的活动？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:624
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_5\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我……我还以为你在这里打开通往其他位面的传送门之类的东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:626
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_5\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他眯起眼睛看着你：“你说什么？我听不太——等一下。”大臣站起身，走向收音机，用铠"
"甲手套迸出的一道能量关掉了它，房间瞬间陷入死寂。他再次转向你：“好吧，不管你打"
"断我们是为了什么，反正我们也差不多要结束了。下周二继续，诸位？”聚集的信徒们纷"
"纷低声应和，随后在一阵刺眼的闪光中尽数消失。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:628
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_5\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "这是怎么回事？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:630
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_5\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"大臣挑了挑眉，指了指桌上摆好的棋局：“嗯？你当真没听说过克尔格瑟克里？”你眨了"
"几下眼，他叹了口气：“我也该料到的。这东西算不上出名，但就算你听过我也不会意外"
"。它算是……某种邪教经典游戏。”他面无表情地盯着你，你完全搞不懂他是不是在等你笑"
"。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:632
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_5\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "勉强笑了笑。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:634
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_5\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "他的眉毛挑得更高了：“我……说了什么好笑的事吗？你没事吧，变元者？进来的时候撞到"
"脑袋了？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:636
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_5\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "呃……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:638
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_5\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你们俩对视了片刻，都一时语塞。最后还是你先撑不住，尴尬地告退，溜进了走廊。刚"
"才那场面……真是糟透了。所有悬而未决的问题里，有一个在你脑海里格外清晰……到底谁"
"会约在周二聚会啊？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:644
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_5\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "保持沉默。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:646
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_5\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "你站在那里，一句话也说不出来，他的眉毛挑得更高了：“你……你还好吗，变元者？进来"
"的时候撞到脑袋了？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:648
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_5\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "呃……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:650
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_5\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你们两人对视了片刻，大臣也和你一样说不出话来。最后还是你先撑不住，尴尬地告辞"
"，快步退到走廊里。刚才那场面……呃，真是糟透了。在所有悬而未决的问题里，有一个"
"在你脑海中挥之不去……到底谁会约在周二聚会啊？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:662
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_5\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "不了。转身离开。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:664
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_5\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"里面到底在搞什么鬼都跟你无关，你可不想被卷进大臣那些诡异仪式的交火里。尽管你"
"已经走远，却依然能听见那低沉的吟唱……仿佛无论你走到哪里，它都如影随形。你耸了"
"耸肩，心想跟一个神秘教派领袖住在一起，会遇上这种事也算是家常便饭了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:669
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_6\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"一道白色残影从你身边飞速掠过，紧接着大臣便跑了过来：“让开，快让开！风暴的一个"
"造物冲破禁锢了！”他转过拐角，仅仅几秒后，拐角处便传来一声爆炸……你必须立刻找掩"
"护！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:671
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_6\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "趴在地上，护住你的头！"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:673
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_GENERIC_6\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你摆出防御姿势，闭上双眼，可……什么都没发生。你抬头一看，惊讶地发现大臣回来了"
"，他铠甲上的靴子在地上拖曳着。他瞥了你一眼：“那个麻烦的家伙已经解决了。非常抱"
"歉打扰到你，变元者。不会再发生这种事了。”他从你身边走过时，语气里带着一丝不屑"
"，只留下你独自躺在地板上。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:678
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_VORTIGON_1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你撞见沃蒂根与大臣正在深入交谈，前者开口道：“所以……你所信奉的这个，呃，风暴。"
"你声称它凌驾于诸圣之上？”他说出“风暴”这个名字时，语气就像被抢走了午餐钱一样。"
"大臣抬手托着下巴，无视了这番轻蔑：“风暴教派内部确实存有水晶。你为何问起这个？"
"难不成你想改信？”沃蒂根发出一阵浑厚的大笑：“我可没这么说，但你证实了我的猜测"
"。你口中的风暴，必定就是一位圣尊，而且比其他任何一位都更为崇高！没想到竟有这"
"种可能……我得去查阅典籍……”他一边思索一边离去，大臣这才注意到你的存在，朝你投来"
"困惑的一瞥。你耸了耸肩。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:681
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_JERRY_1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你虽然没找到大臣，却撞见杰瑞正穿过走廊。他双眼圆睁，像是见了鬼一般，缓缓蹒跚"
"走过时，甚至都没看你一眼。你知道他本就有些木讷古怪……可这副样子，就算对他而言"
"也太反常了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:683
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_JERRY_1\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "试着引起他的注意。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:685
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_JERRY_1\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你喊了他的名字，杰瑞猛地停住脚步，以人类史上最慢的速度转向你。终于，他面向了"
"你，艰难地结结巴巴道：“队、队、队长……那、那个……东、东西，在、在洗手间里……是、"
"是真的吗？真、真的存在吗？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:687
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_JERRY_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "东西？什么东西？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:689
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_JERRY_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"杰瑞花了好几分钟，描述着让他惊魂未定的恐怖景象：一个长着触手的怪物，在黑暗中"
"盯着他。从他的描述里你听得出，那不过是风暴的造物之一，多半是大臣出于某种不为"
"人知的目的放出来的。当然，你可以把这些如实告诉杰瑞，只是……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:691
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_JERRY_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "告诉他真相，并安慰他。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:693
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_JERRY_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你用自己有限的认知，尽量解释了风暴造物的来历，杰瑞眨了好几下眼睛。“那……那没事"
"了？”你点了点头，他夸张地松了一大口气，“太好了，谢天谢地！那下次它……呃……盯着"
"我的时候，我尽量不盯着看就是了。真没想到大人会雇对这种奇怪东西感兴趣的人！”杰"
"瑞走开了，步伐重新恢复了活力，你心里也泛起了一丝极淡的暖意。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:697
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_JERRY_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "编个谎话，逗逗他。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:699
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_JERRY_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你单手托着下巴，装作一副深思熟虑的样子，告诉杰瑞他刚才撞见的恐怕是来自异界的"
"存在。他下巴都惊掉了，怔怔地盯着你片刻，随后双眼一翻，直挺挺倒在地上——杰瑞直"
"接吓晕了。他……居然这么容易被吓到吗？你心里有点过意不去，便给他拿了条毯子，还"
"托人照看他，免得有人在走廊里被他绊倒。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:707
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_JERRY_1\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "别去打扰这个可怜的孩子了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:709
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_JERRY_1\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "显然有什么东西吓到他了，但你觉得最好还是别打扰杰瑞。再说了，万一他只是梦游呢"
"？你可不想打碎他那颗……呃，杰瑞脑袋里正在做的美妙梦境。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:714
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_HAYNES_1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"转过拐角，你看见海因斯正在盘问大臣，而后者只顾摆弄着手里的东西，对这事一点也"
"不上心。\n"
"\n"
"“职业？”\n"
"\n"
"“大臣。”\n"
"“\n"
"效忠对象？”\n"
"\n"
"“风暴。”\n"
"\n"
"“家人？”\n"
"\n"
"“失踪。”\n"
"\n"
"“出生日期？”\n"
"\n"
"“无关紧要。”\n"
"\n"
"海因斯被最后这个回答难住了：“那我们该怎么填表格？你对这份披萨订单的态度，能跟"
"我一样认真点吗？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:734
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_HAYNES_1\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "披萨订单……？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:736
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_HAYNES_1\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"大臣猛地把注意力转向侦探，显然已经忍无可忍：“我倒要问问，送个意大利辣香肠披萨"
"，凭什么需要知道这些东西？难道他们是通过跨次元虫洞送来的？”海因斯双臂交叉：“"
"我怎么知道？我只是在尽力填这破表格而已。”大臣提高了音量：“你不是大名鼎鼎的侦"
"探吗？弄清楚这些不是你的工作？”侦探也上前一步，声音同样拔高：“那你不就是那位"
"大臣吗？你就不能让你那个‘风暴’给你变个披萨出来？”大臣一拳砸在桌上：“你该明白"
"这种琐事根本不值得它费心！还是说你和这里其他人一样蠢？”两人就这样你来我往吵了"
"好一会儿，火气越来越大，你心里隐隐有种预感——你们怕是等不到披萨了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:741
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THESCARRED_1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"虽然这两人未必对彼此抱有敌意，但只要烙疤者和大臣同时在场，房间里就弥漫着一股"
"无法忽视的紧张气氛。你在食堂看到他们面对面坐着，谁也没说一句话，只是各自出神"
"地望着远方。你觉得当着众人的面去打断他们实在太尴尬，但内心深处又很想劝他们放"
"轻松一点——我们的敌人是叛军，不是彼此！不是吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:744
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHUNGER_1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"一阵刺耳的碎裂声吸引了你的注意，你看到大臣正在给饥饿者喂食金属碎片，仿佛它只"
"是一只宠物。最后，饥饿者似乎变得有些暴躁，试图去啃咬大臣的铠甲。就在这时，它"
"那黏糊糊的身体被击飞出去，刺耳的尖叫刺穿了你的耳朵：“不、不、不可食用。仆从？"
"解放者？怎、怎么……怎么会！”大臣轻笑一声，朝踉跄的半械族扔出最后一块金属碎片："
"“真是有趣……我会盯着你的，小家伙。离铠甲远点，听懂了吗？”他自顾自地笑着走开了"
"，饥饿者则摇晃着身体朝你爬来：“舰长……舰、舰、舰长……询问：这是什么？为什么！他"
"、他到底是、是谁……？”你其实也希望自己能弄明白。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:747
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你正走向大臣的房间，一只戴着铠甲的手紧紧抓住你的肩膀，粗暴地把你转过身来面对"
"它的主人。然而令你惊讶的是，站在那里的并不是大臣，而是……女杰。尽管隔着头盔很"
"难看清她的表情，但你能感受到她目光中透出一股就连她本人都少有的强烈气势。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:749
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "你还好吗？出什么事了？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:751
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"女杰抓着你肩膀的手又收紧了几分，她凑近你：“你信任我，对吗？以前你曾为了我对抗"
"邪恶，只是因为我请求了你。只是因为我说那是正确的事，而你选择相信我。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:753
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我是说，没错，可是……这到底是怎么回事？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:755
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"她的声音罕见地有些颤抖：“我……相信我们这艘舰上，又迎来了一股邪恶。你这位大臣，"
"还有那个风暴的造物……他们……浑身都散发着邪恶、欺骗与恶意。我的长矛在他们附近就"
"会灼热发烫，我对此无比确定。可是……”她望向一旁片刻，随后重新与你对视，“他是以"
"盟友的身份来到这里，和我一样，而我信任你的判断……就像你信任我一样。所以，我想"
"问你，战友：你真的相信这位大臣吗？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:757
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "是的，我相信他。我对他的信任，和对你的信任一样深。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:759
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "她放松下来，只是点了点头，然后转身离开。但愿你能像她一样，坚信自己做出的决定"
"。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:763
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "我……我不能说我相信他。我和你有着同样的担忧。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:765
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"女杰再次握紧你的肩膀，狂热的力道几乎要捏碎你的肩骨：“那我们就做英雄最擅长的事"
"。一股新的邪恶必将在今夜覆灭，战友！与我并肩，向它黑暗堡垒的所在地进军，摧毁"
"这玷污我们的污秽。为了多元宇宙！”她手持长矛，朝着大臣房间的方向冲去，而你几乎"
"别无选择，只能跟上前去。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:767
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "追上她。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:769
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"这并不容易，但你还是勉强跟上了她狂热的步伐。你紧跟在女杰身后，她猛地撞开大臣"
"房间的门，大喊道：“现身吧，邪恶，正义终将降临！你的防御已经失效，正义就在你门"
"前！”大臣从椅子上坐直身子，一脸茫然：“你是说被你撞烂的这扇门吗？到底是什么意"
"思？”他越过女杰看向你：“变元者？我建议你看好这个蛮不讲理的家伙，别让她到处随"
"意破坏东西？”她立刻将长矛对准他，大臣的身形瞬间绷紧：“又或者，你和她是一伙的"
"？这就是你所谓的情谊？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:771
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我……呃……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:773
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你还没来得及说上话，女杰就打断了你：“闭嘴，奸贼，否则我就割掉你这条巧舌。”她"
"握紧长矛，你能察觉到长矛在她手中因对准大臣的铠甲而发出灼热的声响。她开口道：“"
"你这身……铠甲，恶魔。我能感受到它的恶意，它对生命以及所有守护生命者的憎恨。你"
"为何要穿上这邪恶之物？”大臣翻了个白眼，立刻对这种夸张的做派感到厌烦：“你是要"
"我闭嘴，还是来审问我的？”一支长矛擦着他的头顶飞过，女杰上前一步：“下一击就不"
"会偏了。说。”大臣脸上先前的不耐烦尽数消失，取而代之的是一种你并非从未见过他流"
"露的情绪：恐惧。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:775
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "这会不会有点太过分了？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:777
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"这一次，你的话传进了她耳中，她的气势稍稍缓和了一些，“原谅我，同志，但这是件严"
"肃的事。他的这套铠甲绝非仅仅是邪恶之物——它就是由邪恶本身铸就的。一种有形的邪"
"恶，堪比那可怕的物质病毒，甚至有过之而无不及……所以我再问你一次，恶魔。你究竟"
"为何要穿戴它？”大臣立刻回答，声音里满是慌乱，“你们这群人疯了吗？关于这套铠甲"
"及其用途，我知道的已经全都说了。它根本不是什么邪恶之物，它就是铠甲！是防具！"
"诚然，它有着难以置信的坚韧，也有着不可言说的危险，但它没有任何自主意识。它只"
"是一件我被迫绑定的物品——我还要补充一句，我对此本身就十分不满，而且它会遵照我"
"的指令行动。至少在大多数情况下是这样，就和所有不稳定的机械一样……”他的声音渐渐"
"低沉，带着一丝悲凉，但女英雄似乎毫不在意，“如果这件邪恶的东西真的在违背你的意"
"愿束缚你，那你就不该对我摧毁它有任何异议。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:779
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你真的能毁掉它吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:781
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“这多元宇宙里没有任何邪恶是我摧毁不了的。这是我的誓言……”你看向大臣，令你惊讶"
"的是，他看上去似乎在考量这种可能性。思索片刻后，他开口道：“你的确非同寻常，可"
"这套铠甲是无法摧毁的。在它强行依附于我时，我就得到了这样的保证，而且……相信我"
"，我试过了。”他叹了口气，继续说道：“如果这样能让你相信我的清白，我不反对移除"
"它，但我担心可能带来的后果。过去我每次试图取下它，铠甲的反应都很不友善。”女杰"
"把他的话听了进去，放下长矛转向你：“我……相信他，同志。即便如此……虽然他本身可能"
"并非邪恶，但那铠甲是。如果你允许，我会试着将它移除。”你看向大臣，他似乎表示同"
"意。现在由你做决定。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:783
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "我们来此是为了铲除邪恶。就让我们把这事做到底。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:785
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"女杰点了点头，转向大臣：“花点时间做好准备。我会将长矛刺入铠甲的核心，也就是它"
"邪恶的源头，尝试从那里粉碎它对你的控制。准备好了就告诉我。”大臣也点了点头，花"
"了片刻平复心神。你看着他翻转双手，注视着自己的护手，然后紧紧握成拳头。如果女"
"英这次成功……他将不仅从铠甲中解脱，或许还能摆脱那场风暴。他可以真心去寻找自己"
"的女儿，将邪教生活的种种恐怖抛在身后。和你、女杰，还有……所有人一起。他会获得"
"真正的自由，你能感觉到他和你一样明白这一点。他深吸一口气，闭上双眼，挺起胸膛"
"：“好了。我准备好了。尽管放手一试吧，英雄。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:787
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:789
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"女杰再次将长矛对准铠甲，厉声喝道：“你这囚笼，纵然没有生命，却依旧邪恶不减。我"
"必将摧毁你，终有一天，我亦会粉碎你那恶毒的主宰。此誓，我必践行。”她摆出击刺姿"
"态，准备发动猛攻，“现在……崩塌吧，囚笼！在你的罪孽重压之下，在我的意志之力面前"
"，碎裂吧！！”女杰以超凡速度疾冲而上，长矛与大臣的铠甲轰然相撞，爆发出雷鸣般的"
"巨响。纤细的光缕从铠甲核心中不断溢出……你意识到，她已然刺穿了它，哪怕只是浅浅"
"一层。她怒吼着，一次、两次、三次地奋力突刺；她的意志化作实质力量，不断加持于"
"身。当她挥出最后决定性一击时，缤纷的光芒自长矛中狂涌而出，然后……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:791
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "然后……？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:793
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"铠甲核心的光芒变得无比刺眼，你的视线瞬间被吞没，唯一能依靠的只剩下听觉。你听"
"见女杰的怒吼，听见大臣在重击之下踉跄后退，还有……混乱之中的第三种声音。一阵低"
"沉的嗡鸣，隐藏在一切声响之下。可你还没来得及辨清来源，大臣就突然尖叫起来：“住"
"手！这套铠甲，它——”他顿了顿，随即因剧痛而抽搐，声音里充满了恐惧，“——我感觉到"
"了！它……呃啊……它要把我撕碎了！！它要杀了我——住手！求你——”女杰也慌忙回应，声音"
"里满是慌乱：“我……我不知道这是怎么回事！我的长矛被死死卡住了……我们是不是做错了"
"……？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:795
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我能做什么……？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:797
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"大臣的惨叫愈发凄厉，他哀求着帮助，哀求着原谅……也哀求着他的女儿。女杰拼命想要"
"施救，却无能为力。比大臣的惨叫更刺耳的，是随之而来的死寂，还有……那阵声音。它"
"此刻愈发强烈，盖过了女杰绝望的呼喊。房间里的光芒越来越盛，亮到远超目眩的程度"
"，你拼命护住双眼。等你再次睁开眼时，光芒已经消失，可是……大臣也不见了。女杰怀"
"里只剩下他的铠甲，如今空空如也。你注意到她的长矛仍嵌在铠甲的核心里，然而……不"
"知为何，它之前造成的所有损伤似乎都已复原，因为你看到核心的外壳已经重新闭合，"
"将长矛牢牢裹在其中。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:800
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/removeCrew/text"
msgstr "你的系统里完全没有留下大臣的任何痕迹……他到底遭遇了什么……？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:803
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你……做了什么……？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:805
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你能听见她带着哭腔回答：“我……我不是……对不起……我没想到——”她话音未落，之前那阵"
"嗡鸣再次袭来，声音越来越大，越来越响。是……那套铠甲。它要爆炸了吗？你再次朝她"
"大喊，让她扔掉铠甲快跑，可……已经太晚了。她转身看向你时，怀中的铠甲再次迸发出"
"一道强光，你被迫再次护住眼睛。等你的视线恢复……女杰也消失了。这一次，连她的铠"
"甲都没留下。只剩下大臣的那套，还有……她的长矛，依旧死死卡在铠甲的核心里。铠甲"
"重重摔落在地，强光过后，只剩下你独自一人。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:808
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/removeCrew/text"
msgstr "女杰也消失得无影无踪。该死……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:811
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "放声呼喊你的朋友们。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:813
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "你不知道还能做些什么，还能做些什么。就在你放声哭喊、宣泄痛苦时，房间里的一个"
"动静吸引了你的注意。那套铠甲刚刚动了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:815
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "什么……？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:817
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"有那么一瞬间，你以为自己只是产生了幻觉，但紧接着，一切又再次发生。铠甲的手指"
"开始抽搐，随后是双腿，接着是整个身躯。它剧烈痉挛、猛地抽动，动作越来越剧烈，"
"然后……突然僵住，四肢笔直，开始缓缓浮空。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:819
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "我是不是疯了？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:821
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"铠甲以一种仿佛有意识的姿态转向你。它的护手伸出，抓住胸口里的长矛，就这么……拔"
"了出来。在它行动的同时，核心的伤口自动愈合，看上去就像从未被刺穿一样。它将长"
"矛扔到地上，继续面对着你。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:823
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你是什么东西？你把我的朋友们怎么样了？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:825
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"它的核心黯淡下去，随即闪烁起来，接着猛然爆发出强光，整个房间再次被一片白光吞"
"没。这一次……消失的是那套铠甲，但并非没有留下任何痕迹。你检查飞船系统时发现，"
"它为你留下了一段可读取的数据……一组坐标。你的理智在尖叫，告诉你这必定是个陷阱"
"，可你内心却因失踪的伙伴们而剧痛不已。只要有一丝可能他们就在这些坐标之处，或"
"是你能在那里为他们复仇，你都愿意一试。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:827
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "别担心……我来了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:849
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "我觉得这不值得冒这个险。我们应该想想别的办法。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:851
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_MINISTER_THEHEROINE_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"两人不情愿地同意了，局势暂时平息下来。如果大臣对那次针对他性命的袭击一直耿耿"
"于怀，他并没有表现出来，但……整件事还是让你感到尴尬。而且，女杰所说的关于大臣"
"铠甲的话，仍在你脑海中回荡。那东西真的会是一个由纯粹的仇恨构成的存在吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:887
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_HEROINE_NOTHING\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你试图引起她的注意，可女杰似乎正忙着在飞船里追一只老鼠。她完全没理会你，只是"
"在那只老鼠跑得比她快时对着它大喊：“你尽管逃吧，卑劣的害虫，但你给我记住。正义"
"——永不停歇！你那传染性的恐怖统治，到此结束了！！”至少她玩得挺开心。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:890
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_HEROINE_GENERIC_1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你正在寻找女杰，这时一阵巨响吸引了你的注意……听起来像是玻璃被砸碎的声音。循着"
"声音，你来到了自助餐厅，果不其然，女杰正把餐具狠狠砸在地上。她一边砸一边大喊"
"：“自由吧，玻璃之民！你们再也不会被人类的随心所欲束缚，再也不会为了所谓的‘便"
"利’被迫辛劳劳作。食物理应用双手捧着，而不是靠这些被奴役的器物！”她这场英勇的“"
"暴动”持续了很久，你不禁开始疑惑，如果所有玻璃制品都象征着残酷，那她平时到底要"
"怎么使用任何东西。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:893
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_HEROINE_GENERIC_2\"]/text"
msgstr "女杰朝你走来，手里拿着一本书：“我在你的住处地上捡到了这个。我没让它落上灰尘，"
"不过……告诉我，同志，你真的会看书吗？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:895
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_HEROINE_GENERIC_2\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "怎么了？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:897
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_HEROINE_GENERIC_2\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"她点了点头，凑近过来，一边把书递给你一边说：“那就别担心了，同志。你是个书呆子"
"这个秘密，我会烂在肚子里。”她拍了拍你的后背就走开了，可你敢发誓，她刚才在拼命"
"憋笑……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:901
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_HEROINE_GENERIC_2\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "不是吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:903
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_HEROINE_GENERIC_2\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"她的姿态瞬间绷紧，空着的那只手拔出了长矛：“你是说，这艘飞船上藏着一个秘密书呆"
"子，在你的住处偷偷看书？！”女杰快步冲了出去，脚步带着力量，一边跑一边大喊：“"
"出来吧，虚伪的书呆子！在正义面前，你无处可藏！！”你敢肯定，她其实在拼命憋笑……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:908
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_HEROINE_GENERIC_3\"]/text"
msgstr "你发现女杰昏睡在床上，铠甲仍穿在身上，这让你意识到你从未见过她卸下铠甲……她身"
"旁放着手机，屏幕还没有进入休眠模式。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:910
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_HEROINE_GENERIC_3\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "偷偷看一眼她的手机。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:912
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_HEROINE_GENERIC_3\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你小心翼翼地越过女杰，尽量不发出动静，从她身边拿起了手机。翻看之后，你发现她"
"正在浏览鱼的照片……她居然真的在飞船数据库里搜索了“鱼”这个词。虽然你不明白原因"
"，但把手机放回原处、迅速离开房间时，还是感到有些尴尬。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:916
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_HEROINE_GENERIC_3\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "给她盖上一条毯子。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:918
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_HEROINE_GENERIC_3\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你在给女杰盖上一条温暖毯子时想起，大多数鱼类都是冷血动物；你可不能让这位多元"
"宇宙的勇士感冒啊！前提是……深渊潜者会感冒吗？你盖毯子时她轻轻动了动，在睡梦中"
"喃喃自语：“倒下吧……zzz……你这个笨蛋反派……zzzz……给我碾碎……呼噜呼噜呼呼……在我无"
"与伦比的力量之下……zzzzz……”她甚至真的把“呼噜呼噜呼呼”这几个音念了出来。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:922
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_HEROINE_GENERIC_3\"]/choice[3]/text"
msgstr "别打扰她。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:924
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_HEROINE_GENERIC_3\"]/choice[3]/event/text"
msgstr "她在睡觉，没有理由去打扰她……穿着那样一副铠甲入睡肯定不容易。你轻手轻脚地离开"
"了房间，而她只是继续打着呼噜。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:929
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_HEROINE_GENERIC_4\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"女杰在她的房间里，看样子正在锻炼。你很难想象穿着这身铠甲做运动有多轻松……她刚"
"完成一个三周后空翻就注意到了你，随即停下脚步：“同志！过来，和我一起练！”她指"
"了指身旁一个200公斤的哑铃，你注意到那个哑铃几乎要把它下面的支架压垮了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:931
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_HEROINE_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "好吧，我……呃……尽力而为？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:933
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_HEROINE_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你抓起哑铃时，她在一旁为你加油，你闭上双眼……你的一生仿佛都在为此刻做准备。你"
"凝聚起体内所有的力量向上举起，而令你惊讶的是……这感觉……毫不费力？！你震惊地把"
"哑铃丢了下去，它砸进地板里，差点砸到你的脚，女杰在你身后大笑道：“好样的！就是"
"这股劲头！”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:935
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_HEROINE_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "搞什么？我怎么做到的？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:937
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_HEROINE_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"女杰拍了拍那只仍微微陷在地板里的哑铃：“你可知道，这可不是普通的重物！！这是属"
"于英雄的负重……它既能锤炼身躯，也能磨砺意志，并且会做出相应的回应。真正的英雄"
"两者都看重——这些负重也是如此！以你这样的胳膊能把它举起来，同志，你的精神一定"
"无比强大！”她再次笑了起来，你努力不去理会那句小小的调侃，两人一起训练了一会儿"
"。等到训练结束时，无论你的身体还是精神，都仿佛被力量点燃……又或者，那只是你的"
"肌肉在拼命哀嚎。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:943
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_HEROINE_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "我就不啦，谢谢。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:945
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_HEROINE_GENERIC_4\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"她耸了耸肩：“好吧，不过别松懈训练，同志……邪恶随时都可能来袭！！”是啊，你可不"
"想在刚举完比自己还重的东西、累得筋疲力尽的时候，偏偏遇上邪恶来袭！！你以后……"
"还是慢跑之类的算了吧？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:950
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_HEROINE_FREDDY_1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你在休息室找到弗雷迪和女杰时，两人正捧着茶相谈甚欢，聊得十分投入。弗雷迪微微"
"向她脱帽致意，开口说道：“说实话，这真是段愉快的时光。我没什么机会和深渊潜者交"
"流，但就我接触过的那些而言，你在交谈上要……怎么说呢……热情得多。”女杰猛地把茶杯"
"按在脸上，茶水从她的面甲缝隙渗了进去：“你真这么觉得？！太谢谢你了，同志！我老"
"家的亲人很快就会嫌我话多。”弗雷迪看着碎掉的茶杯，清了清嗓子：“是啊，嗯……我们"
"有时候确实都会有点过激，我敢肯定。”他们又聊了很久，又有好几个茶杯惨遭“毒手”，"
"你决定在被玻璃碎片溅到之前赶紧离开房间。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:953
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_HEROINE_EATER_1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"eater从你身边跑过，手里拿着一根被咬了一半的长矛，女杰紧随其后追了上来。两人转"
"过拐角，你听见她在后面大喊：“立刻把我的长矛还回来，同志！！长矛是用来消灭邪恶"
"的，不是用来满足食欲的！！”你……呃……相信他们总会解决的。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:956
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_HEROINE_NIGHTS_1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你正漫步在走廊里，七夜从你身旁走过，黏滑的皮肤上插着好几根长矛。你问他这是怎"
"么回事，他不情愿地解释道：“就是那个鱼女杰，穿铠甲的那个疯子？我当时正在吃早餐"
"，像往常一样喝了几杯啤酒，她就突然开始追我，扔长矛，还叫我‘吸食纯粹邪恶之人’"
"之类的。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:958
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_HEROINE_NIGHTS_1\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "哇，这，呃……听起来真的太惨了。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:960
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_HEROINE_NIGHTS_1\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他试图拔出其中一根长矛，可它牢牢卡在他的黏液里。“她到底从哪儿弄来这些东西……天"
"啊，我喝得再多点都顶不住这个……七夜蠕动着离开，嘴里嘟囔着自己的悲惨遭遇，你忍"
"不住觉得这场景有点好笑。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:964
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_HEROINE_NIGHTS_1\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "也许这是戒酒的好理由？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:966
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_HEROINE_NIGHTS_1\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"他看着你，仿佛你说了他听过最蠢的话：“戒酒的好理由——根本没有戒酒的好理由。要是"
"真说有什么，这只会让我更想喝酒……”七夜蠕动着离开，嘴里嘟囔着自己的悲惨遭遇，你"
"忍不住觉得这场景有点好笑。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:971
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_HEROINE_THESCARRED_1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你撞见女杰和烙疤者正坐在一起，全神贯注地冥想。两位深渊潜者一同哼着低沉而粗犷"
"的曲调，你能感觉到自己不该打扰他们。之后你向烙疤者询问他们刚才在做什么，你敢"
"肯定，当他们将其描述为“一场对其族人而言神圣的仪式”时，脸颊微微泛红。你暗自庆"
"幸，还好刚才没有打断他们……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:983
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_SHADE_NOTHING\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"虽然你成功找到了躲在角落里的暗影，但它对你的存在没有丝毫反应。它只是凝视着远"
"方——似乎什么也没有看。考虑到你之前多次尝试与它互动都得到类似的回应，这并不令"
"人意外，但你仍忍不住希望它这副失神的模样能有所改变……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:986
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_SHADE_GENERIC_1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"你打开电灯开关，却被吓了一跳——暗影的身影就出现在你面前几英寸远的地方。出于习"
"惯，你紧张地为差点撞到它而道歉，它当然毫无反应，只是……站在那里。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:988
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_SHADE_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "尴尬地盯着它看。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:990
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_SHADE_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"当你凝视着这个身披斗篷的黑暗身影时，一部分的你感到心神不宁……但另一部分的你却"
"充满好奇。在如此近的距离下，你能辨认出它周身模糊、难以辨认的刻痕——一系列漩涡"
"、圆点和棱角分明的线条，当你的目光追随这些神秘图案流转时，它们几乎像是构成了"
"某种纹路。这股流转并未如你所想般在边缘处中断，而是径直延续到下一处，仿佛暗影"
"的整个身躯都被当作了一幅画布。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:992
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_SHADE_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "继续研究这些奇怪的符号。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:994
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_SHADE_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"有那么一会儿，你就只是绕着暗影打转，一边仔细研究着那些令人困惑的刻痕。你觉得"
"，如果说有什么地方能成为了解它身份、或是它目的的关键线索，那从这里入手再合适"
"不过了。可过了一阵子……你忽然察觉到一件事。你并没有认出这些刻痕，也没有奇迹般"
"读懂它们的含义——但你发现，越是盯着它们看，心里就越生出一种熟悉感。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:996
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_SHADE_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "专心去感受你心底的那份异样感觉。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:998
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_SHADE_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你很快就弄清了这股奇怪直觉的根源——这些纹路看上去就像是一幅星图。或许这些星辰"
"对你而言完全陌生，但你这辈子见过的星图已经足够多，足以让你对自己的观察十分确"
"定。为什么暗影会在它的金属躯体上刻下星图，又或者这星图究竟有何意义，至今仍是"
"个彻头彻尾的谜——但你感觉自己离解开这个谜又近了好几步。心满意足的你决定暂时不"
"去打扰它，而在你转身离开，任由它继续那些不为人知的行动时，暗影连动都没有动一"
"下。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1006
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_SHADE_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "移开目光，转身离开。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1008
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_SHADE_GENERIC_1\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr "这东西让你毛骨悚然……你赶紧远离它，在你关掉灯、匆忙离开房间时，暗影依旧纹丝不"
"动。这家伙到底是怎么回事？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1013
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_SHADE_THESCARRED_1\"]/text"
msgstr "你正轻轻敲着暗影那温热的金属斗篷，这时烙疤者走进了房间。他们很快就注意到你在"
"摆弄这个怪异的存在，随即向你投来好奇的目光。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1015
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_SHADE_THESCARRED_1\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "你盯着我干什么？我只是……想弄明白这东西而已，不行吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1017
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_SHADE_THESCARRED_1\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"烙疤者被你这戒备的样子逗得轻笑一声，走到你身边，和你一起看着一动不动的暗影。"
"他仔细打量了一番，像是在思索着什么，然后转向你：“它……很迷人，不是吗？一个绝妙"
"的谜团……我唯一担心的是，伪神……正是在赌这一点——我们的……好奇心。这……东西显然是"
"他造出来的，可……目的又是什么？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1019
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_SHADE_THESCARRED_1\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "你有什么猜测吗？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1021
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_SHADE_THESCARRED_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"独眼深渊潜者认真地思索着你的问题，又陷入了一阵沉思。随后，忧虑之色浮现于面容"
"，“我……怀疑这确实是个陷阱。若非……意在取我们性命，那或许……便是为满足其私欲而设"
"。”\n"
"\n"
"烙疤者顿了顿，神色愈发凝重，“若由我抉择……我必毁掉这机器。但……虚伪辉光想必……深"
"知这一点，正如其知晓……这选择权不在我手中。无论你……作何决定，族人……我只愿你遵"
"从本心——而非为任何……自封的神明。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1025
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_SHADE_THESCARRED_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "当然。我保证到时候会凭心而行。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1027
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_SHADE_THESCARRED_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你诚恳地对烙疤者说着，看着对方的表情缓和了下来。“那……我便没什么好担心的了。一"
"如既往，我……与你同在，族人。”说完，他们便离开了房间，只留下你与那个永远喋喋不"
"休的暗影再度独处。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1031
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_SHADE_THESCARRED_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "你无法做出任何承诺。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1033
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_SHADE_THESCARRED_1\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你的回答似乎让烙疤者微微有些失望，但他们还是理解地点了点头。“有……很长很长的时"
"光，我也曾……沉迷于虚伪辉光的馈赠。沉迷于它的……许诺。那些许诺如今……只余破碎，"
"与遗忘。但愿，无论……此物为何，无论它的存在将引我们走向何方……我们不会落得同样"
"破碎、同样被遗忘的下场。”说完，他们便离开了房间，只留下你与那个永远喋喋不休的"
"暗影，思索着烙疤者的话语。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1043
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_LIST_SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/text[1]"
msgstr "……你回来了，求见我，碎灰者。你有父亲的消息吗？他近来似乎总是……心事重重。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1044
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_LIST_SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/text[2]"
msgstr "……我们又一次在此相见，在这界中之界……一个既非物质、也非冥影位面的地方。在这里"
"，我们可以畅所欲言，穹弑者。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1045
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_LIST_SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/text[3]"
msgstr "……你竟能让星辰重获生机，却仍在追寻更高的目标……我渴望能与你这份野心比肩，执刃"
"者！为了母亲……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1046
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_LIST_SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/text[4]"
msgstr ""
"作为您的利刃、父亲的利刃——乃至母亲的利刃……回应您的每一声召唤，是我的职责。此"
"心至死不渝，直至那宿命之舞降临的一日；直至刀剑、护盾与羽翼再无存在之必要，多"
"元宇宙永享安宁。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1047
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_LIST_SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/text[5]"
msgstr ""
"……它们难道不美吗，执刃者？你所守护的这些色彩——你族人的笑容……我终于明白，你为"
"何要如此英勇地奋战，去守护这一切。真希望母亲也能如她所愿，亲眼看见这一切……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1048
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//textList[@name=\"TEXT_LIST_SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/text[6]"
msgstr ""
"……你的时机一如既往地完美无缺……连空间裂隙都在不安中轰鸣！它们早已期待这场对话"
"。即便如此，我们相聚的时间或许依旧短暂——你有何烦心事，碎灰者？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1051
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/text"
msgstr "色彩、质感、温度——这些由感官赋予你的微小慰藉，每一样都曾被你视作理所当然……当"
"你靠近监管者时，它们仿佛全都消散了，然后……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1055
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/text"
msgstr "继续。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1057
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1059
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1061
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1063
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1067
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "想象一个问题——它自由飘浮，永不停歇地追寻着答案。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1069
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr "原来你也心生好奇了！我会尽力给你一个交代。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1071
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"unique_thescarred\"]/text"
msgstr "想象一条鱼——只有一只眼睛，也正因如此，它变得更加盲目。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1073
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"unique_thescarred\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"我对你的朋友并无多少敌意——作为你的利刃，我无权如此。可是父亲……他憎恶他们。正"
"是他们，那些叛徒，真正摧毁了我——也正因如此，他们才该为我妹妹如今的状况负上最"
"终责任。因为他们的恶行，父亲的宿命之舞被推迟了。多元宇宙亦是如此……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1075
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"unique_thescarred\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1077
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"unique_thescarred\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……不过，我离题了。我们在此的时间已所剩无几——直到下次再会，我的持有者……好好运"
"用我，还有我的容器。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1083
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"unique_thehunger\"]/text"
msgstr "想象一张巨口——无论在规模还是贪婪之上，都永无止境。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1085
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"unique_thehunger\"]/event/text"
msgstr "父亲认为此人颇具价值……在他眼中，他们已经证明了自己。若是他们能更早达成约定——"
"或许本可以晋升，真心实意地执掌我，彻底避免我碎裂的结局……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1087
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"unique_thehunger\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1089
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"unique_thehunger\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……只是我偏题了。我们在此的时光已近尾声——下次再会，我的持有者……好好驾驭我，也"
"好好驾驭我的容器。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1095
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theaberration\"]/text"
msgstr "想象一个弄臣——一个愚人，在国王的宫廷里被当作笑料……最终却被弃之不顾。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1097
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theaberration\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"我不像父亲那样轻视这个人——因为我知道母亲不会如此。与自己的命运抗争并无多少耻"
"辱可言，即便那命运是他们自己造就的。即便如此，主动向父亲挑起争端……实在太过鲁"
"莽。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1099
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theaberration\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1101
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theaberration\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……只是我偏题了。我们在此的时间已经不多——下次再会，我的持有者……好好运用我，也"
"好好运用我的容器。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1107
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\"]/text"
msgstr "想象一位夜爵士——他们熠熠生辉的铠甲之下，藏着血肉，也藏着秘密……两者分量相当。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1109
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\"]/event/text"
msgstr "这个人……让我想起了母亲。一种奇异的感觉，温暖又带着忧伤。不过，考虑到他们如此"
"相似，也就难怪父亲会憎恨这个人了……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1111
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1113
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theheroine\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……只是我偏题了。我们在此的时间已经不多——下次再会，我的持有者……请好好运用我，"
"也好好运用我的容器。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1119
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theminister\"]/text"
msgstr "想象一位亲人——迷失在黑暗中，步履踉跄，却仍能强作镇定，露出坚强的面容。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1121
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theminister\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"父亲已指定此人执掌我的另一位姐妹，他的双翼，可是……我担心这并非奖赏，而是一种"
"惩罚。尽管这位“大臣”宁愿装作并非如此，我却能看出……在内心深处，他和母亲当年一"
"模一样……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1123
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theminister\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1125
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"ddunique_theminister\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……不过我言尽于此了。我们在此的时光已然不多——下次再会，我的持有者……请好好运用"
"我，也好好运用我的容器。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1131
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\"]/text"
msgstr "想象一只鸟——它生有雷霆万钧的巨翼，为黎明将至而鸣警。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1133
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"父亲的羽翼……没想到你不仅能找到我，还能找到我那更偏向野兽形态的妹妹……你的确令"
"人叹服，穹弑者。但我恐怕，他的盾牌不会这么容易被找到——父亲似乎执意要将她留在"
"身边。更不必说她所承受的……惩戒……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1135
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1137
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDULTIMAARMOR\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……不过，我离题了。我们在此的时间已经不多——待到下次再会，我的持有者……好好驾驭"
"我，也好好驾驭我的容器。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1143
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDSERAPHIM\"]/text"
msgstr "想象一位天使——并非由水晶构成，也非出自黑暗阴谋，而是源于神圣的侍奉。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1145
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDSERAPHIM\"]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"我相信这些存在里，大多数都对父亲的伎俩一无所知。而那些知情者，似乎都遭到了嘲"
"讽——被驱逐，流放到其他的现实之中……不过，这是你我之间的悄悄话，碎灰者？我倒是"
"认同这位被放逐者后半段的想法——我也希望能再次见到母亲……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1147
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDSERAPHIM\"]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1149
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[@req=\"LIST_CREW_DDSERAPHIM\"]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……不过，我言尽于此。我们在此的时光已所剩无几——待到下次再会，我的持有者……好好"
"运用我，也好好驾驭我的容器。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1155
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[8]/text"
msgstr "想象一名囚徒——一位满怀牵挂的姐姐，身陷无边、黑暗而扭曲的空间。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1157
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[8]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"我的妹妹……？虽然她所受的苦难并非徒劳，可我……我宁愿受苦的是我。她被父亲留在身"
"边已经太久太久了，而——尽管我相信他的所作所为，相信他那场仪式的承诺——我还是忍"
"不住希望，在他那永恒的乐园里能有她的一席之地。无论如何，我最开心的，是有幸再"
"次听见她的声音……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1159
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[8]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1161
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[8]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……不过，我言归正传。我们在此的时间已经不多——待到下次再会，我的持有者……好好驾"
"驭我，也好好驾驭我的容器。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1167
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[9]/text"
msgstr "想象一只眼——始终注视，始终存在，始终审判。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1169
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[9]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"无论父亲是否认可你过去或未来的所作所为，我发誓都会站在你这边，碎灰者。父亲或"
"许常常……显得严苛，但……我从未认为他心怀恶意。对此我深信不疑——我只祈祷，假以时"
"日，你能像我一样彻底信任他……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1171
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[9]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1173
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[9]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……不过，我言归正传。我们在此的时间已经不多——待到下次再会，我的持有者……好好运"
"用我，也好好守护我的容器。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1179
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[10]/text"
msgstr "想象一具遗骸——曾经无比辉煌的存在，如今沦为星尘中的残砾。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1181
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[10]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"没错，大天使们及其可怖的阴谋已然落败。即便他们的算计曾让母亲获得些许自由，我"
"也难以想象，在他们那亵渎神明的计划中，等待着母亲与冥影位面的将会是何等可怕的"
"命运。不过，随着他们的覆灭，维持位面的秩序将会变得异常艰难……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1183
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[10]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1185
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[10]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……不过，我言归正传。我们在此的时间已经不多——待到下次再会，我的持有者……好好运"
"用我，也好好守护我的容器。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1191
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[11]/text"
msgstr "想象一个国度——在挣脱束缚之后，依旧美得动人心魄。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1193
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[11]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"冥影位面……唉，我多希望事情不曾走到这一步。仅凭我一人，该如何唤醒光裔族？我知"
"道父亲信任我，可是……我还是忍不住害怕，我会再次让他失望。害怕历史会重演，比上"
"一次更加真实，而位面那些绚烂的色彩，将会再一次彻底消散……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1195
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[11]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1197
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[11]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……不过，我言归正传。我们在此的时间已经不多——待到下次再会，我的持有者……好好运"
"用我，也好好守护我的容器。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1203
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[12]/text"
msgstr "想象一座钟——它滴答作响的宿命，无人能够逃避。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1205
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[12]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"当我们相伴的时光走向尽头，我会回到我的位面——毕竟，光裔族需要指引。不过，执刃"
"者……倘若你真的有需要，我会尽我所能回应你的呼唤。我……我知道，我的妹妹也会希望"
"如此。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1207
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[12]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "..."

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1209
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice[12]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "……不过，我言归正传。我们在此的时间已然不多——待到下次再会，我的持有者……好好运"
"用我，也好好守护我的容器。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1217
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "想象一只杯子——空无一物，亦无任何用意。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1219
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$//event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER\"]/choice/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"只是一句问候而已吗？好吧，你好，持有者。说实话，我还挺喜欢这些不那么……沉重的"
"交谈。我相信，我的妹妹也会喜欢的。那么，下次再会——好好运用我，也好好守护我的"
"容器。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1230
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER_THESCARRED_1\"]/text"
msgstr "你没花多久就找到了那位怪异的深渊潜者，他坐在离监管者及其诡异的空间影响结界不"
"远的地方。你一靠近，那位带伤疤的存在便招呼你过去。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1232
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER_THESCARRED_1\"]/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "遵命，坐到他们身边。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1234
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER_THESCARRED_1\"]/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你毫不犹豫地坐到烙疤者身旁，他们将你的注意力引向那具静止不动的自动人偶。“同族"
"……我们穿越这片‘冥影位面’的旅程……已经揭示了许多真相。关于伪神的本质、他的圣物…"
"…还有，令我意外的是，我过往的一些碎片。这把剑……我现在记起来了。我记得……我曾听"
"闻的一切。记得……我曾做过的事。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1236
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER_THESCARRED_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "嗯，我在听……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1238
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER_THESCARRED_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"深渊潜者沉吟片刻，继续说道：“我本应持有那件圣物……伪神是如此期望的。我的升华……"
"我曾如此热切地期盼，可是……它在向我尖叫。在伪神机械外壳的深处，有什么东西就在"
"附近……它尖叫着发出警告。警告……关于那场仪式，关于万物的终结……关于这位‘黑暗之神"
"’真正的内里。尽管细节依旧……模糊不清，但我仿佛仍能清晰听见它的哀求……它恳求我拿"
"起这把剑，然后……摧毁它。终结这一切……或者，至少延缓那看似无可避免的命运。直到…"
"…有谁，或是有什么东西，能彻底阻止伪神。”\n"
"\n"
"沉默持续了一会儿，你不禁猜测深渊潜者正在回忆什么。随即，他们的脸色沉了下来，"
"直视着你的眼睛：“我担心……我们修复了这把剑，反倒只是在推动伪神……他自己的阴谋。"
"”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1242
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER_THESCARRED_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/text"
msgstr "这些信息一时难以消化，可是……你为什么会突然想起这一切？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1244
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER_THESCARRED_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr "他们的目光移开，重新望向监管者：“在那个诡异的位面里……一切都显得混沌不清……可唯"
"有一件事格外清晰——一个声音……你也听见了，对吗？”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1246
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER_THESCARRED_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/text"
msgstr "是的，我听到了。那面盾牌……"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1248
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER_THESCARRED_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“它……真是这么说的吗？说实在的，我只和它短暂交谈过，但……这些事也是它告诉我的。"
"我过往的这些秘密……它认为是伪神亲自……把它们从我记忆里藏了起来。了解它之后，我"
"倾向于相信……这个陌生的声音。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1250
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER_THESCARRED_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "那么，我们现在该怎么办？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1252
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER_THESCARRED_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[1]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"烙疤者深吸一口气，点了点头：“我们……一直在做的事——必须继续去了解……尽我们所能。"
"我们如今亲眼所见……即便是自称为神的存在，也会流血。”\n"
"\n"
"他们从座位上起身，离开了房间，只留下你独自面对着监管者的容器所发出的异界嗡鸣…"
"…为何黑暗之神在交出剑刃一事上改变了主意，却仍保留着它的盾牌？而如果她真的被困"
"住了……你还能找到她吗？这些问题，连同更多的疑惑，都没能从头顶的星辰中得到多少"
"答案……唯有那令人烦躁的嗡鸣不断回响。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1260
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER_THESCARRED_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "保持安静。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1262
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER_THESCARRED_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"“我不建议我们互相隐瞒，同族，只是……无论如何，是它向我揭示了这一切。我过往的这"
"些秘密……它认为是伪神亲自……将它们从我这里隐藏起来。知道这点后，我倾向于相信……"
"这个陌生的声音。”"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1264
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER_THESCARRED_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/text"
msgstr "那么，我们现在该怎么办？"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1266
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER_THESCARRED_1\"]/choice[1]/event/choice/event/choice/event/choice[2]/event/choice/event/text"
msgstr ""
"烙疤者深吸一口气，然后点了点头，“我们……一直在做的事——我们必须继续去了解……尽我"
"们所能。我们如今已经亲眼见证……即便是自称为神的存在，也会流血。”\n"
"\n"
"他们从座位上起身，离开了房间，只留下你独自承受着监管者容器传来的异界嗡鸣……为"
"何黑暗之神改变了交出剑刃的主意，却仍旧保留着它的盾牌？而如果她早已被困……你还"
"能找到她吗？这些疑问，连同更多未解之谜，都没能从头顶的星辰中得到多少答案……唯"
"有那令人烦躁的嗡鸣依旧回荡。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1280
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER_THESCARRED_1\"]/choice[2]/text"
msgstr "逃跑。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1282
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER_THESCARRED_1\"]/choice[2]/event/text"
msgstr ""
"你今天已经受够了这些诡异又夸张的对话，你受够了！你要回到太空去，该死！是正常"
"的那种太空——没有灰度画面、没有盯着你的眼球状星辰、也没有会回望你的星云——只有"
"舒适、美好、熟悉的太空！你趁机脱身逃走，你确信烙疤者此刻一定一脸困惑，但你现"
"在根本不在乎。"

#: src-en/data/events_special_socialize.xml.append:1287
msgid ""
"data/events_special_socialize.xml.append$/dummyroot/event[@name=\"SOCIALIZE_DDTHE_OVERSEER_THEMINISTER_1\"]/text"
msgstr ""
"在监管者身旁，你找到了大臣——他一边记录笔记，一边摆弄着几件工具，却仍刻意与她"
"那诡异的气场保持着足够的距离。你路过时，他并未留意你，你也选择不去打扰他的摆"
"弄，但你能猜出他心中所想……那柄剑、那双翅膀——还有预言。尽管他在其中扮演的角色"
"对所有人而言都模糊不清，尤其是对他自己，你猜想他一心想要弄清真相。在这一点上"
"，你与大臣感同身受……你也尚未弄明白，自己在这场疯狂之中究竟扮演着怎样的角色。"
